by all but the most dedicated researchers with even less known about his life history beyond brief synopses associated with the books and replicated in various book descriptions see alsoedit organic farming biodynamic agriculture compost list of sustainable agriculture topics referencesedit  a b c stinner dh  the science of organic farming in william lockeretz organic farming an international history oxfordshire uk  cambridge massachusetts cab international cabi pp – isbn  retrieved  august   ebook isbn   a b c howard louise e  sir albert howard in india london faber  faber retrieved  august   pdf version  notification of knighthood conferred  june  the london gazette no   july  retrieved  august    rebecca jones green harvest the history of organic farming and gardening in australia collingwood victoria csiro publishing  p   solomon steve sir albert howards indore method organic gardeners composting soil and health library archived from the original on  may  retrieved    a b vogt g  the origins of organic farming in william lockeretz organic farming an international history oxfordshire uk  cambridge massachusetts cab international cabi pp – isbn  retrieved  august   ebook isbn   jackson wes piper jon december  the necessary marriage between ecology and agriculture pdf ecology   – doi retrieved  august   jstor citation for page accuracy  jackson wes  natural systems agriculture a truly radical alternative pdf agricultural ecosystems and environment   – doisx retrieved  august    a b sayre laura  march  review the origins of the organic movement rodale institute retrieved  august    mantle paul two reviews see review of origins of the organic movement tributes the man of the trees richard st barbe baker p  retrieved  august    lotter dw organic agriculture j sustainable agriculture   an agricultural testament  out of print description of an agricultural testament description is verbatim from rear of dustcover cumberland books website archived from the original on  no