 lakeshore engineering from  to  and again from  to  munising wood products cleveland cliff and cliff dow chemical company he also worked as a car salesman for specker motors in marquette he enjoyed hunting fishing and bowling in  he and his wife moved to antigo to be near their daughter and are members of antigo united methodist church survivors include his wife irene and daughter barbara arnold both of antigo he was preceded in death by his parents son in law joseph arnold one brother william one sister elaine weitzel services will be held on sunday march    pm at antigo united methodist church with rev jason dickerson officiating visitation will be held at the church on sunday from    pm bradley funeral home is assisting the family with arrangements posting as who are you posting as     post tribute post privatelythere are no tributes yet we encourage you to show your support by adding a tribute aboveshare your favorite memory of albertoffer your condolences to the familylight a virtual candle videosthere are no videos to displayphotos add a photo the services for albert have not yet been added please sign up below to be notified when the services are ready get notified when a service is added have a floral question call      items   categories home product listing product details cart sort by defaultname a  zname z  aprice low  highprice high  low healing registry unavailable at the moment displaying page  of  products  to of loading product name description   add to cart your shopping cart is empty select a recipient jane doe ×whats your email address what would you like written on the cardchoose a delivery date  note delivery is only available on highlighted dates for flowers only sunday delivery will not be available on all flower purchases where would you like to deliver to   visitationservice   other select a statealabamaalaskaarizonaarkansascaliforniacoloradoconnecticutdelawaredistrict of columbiafloridageorgiahawaiiidahoillinoisindianaiowakansaskentuckylo